        <Parent_String>cornice components [300001797], cornices and cornice components [300052250], entablature components [300001779], entablatures and entablature components [300052249], spanning and projecting structural elements [300078049], structural elements [300078048], structural elements and components for structural elements [300078046], architectural elements [300000885], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
